 One week ago I reread the official docs and realized that Solidity code can be compiled online using the Remix editor, but Zama-layer’s TypeScript development environment must be set up locally — I only started creating the local TypeScript environment today.

(一周过去，我反复读了好几遍官方文档，终于明白过来，Solidity代码部分可以直接在Remix在线智能合约部署平台直接部署。但链下使用的Zama中继器加密与解密服务的访问必须使用TypeScript环境，这就只能在本地创建编程环境了。于是今天才开始创建TypeScript编程环境。)

Step 1 (第一步)

Installing NVM(node.js version management) (安装NVM(node.js 版本 管理器))

https://github.com/coreybutler/nvm-windows#installation--upgrades

I installed the application on the D: drive. (我把它安装在D盘。)

When selecting the default installation directory for Node.js,I also chose the D: drive.

(当要求选择默认的Node.js环境目录时，我仍然选择了D盘。)

Step2 (第二步)

Installing Node.js （安装Node.js）

After installing Node.js, check whether the installation was successful.

(After installing Node.js, verify that it installed correctly.)

(After Node.js is installed, confirm the installation succeeded.)

(在安装Node.js之后，检查一下是否安装成功。)

nvm list
	

查看已安装的 Node.js 版本

nvm install <version>
	

安装指定版本的 Node.js

nvm use <version>
	

使用指定版本的 Node.js

nvm alias default <version>
	

设置默认 Node.js 版本

nvm uninstall <version>
	

卸载指定版本的 Node.js

nvm ls
nvm list available
nvm 20.19.6 //TCL version // an even-numbered version (e.g., v18.x, v20.x) (只能是偶数版本号)
nvm use  20.19.6
//check: (verify) (检查，不是体检checkup)
node -v
npm -v
